Package com.nickbenn.onehundred

Base package for classes and interfaces making up the implementation of One Hundred. Any class located directly in this package is an entry point suitable for launch as a Java application—that is, such a class has a public static void main(String[] args) method.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConsoleMain
    Implements entry point for console-mode implementation of "One Hundred", a simple form of the Nim category of mathematical games.
